{
  "video_id": "jdpIKXLLYYM",
  "title": "How to make work-life balance work | Nigel Marsh",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 17259.0,
      "text": "What I thought I would do"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17260.0,
      "end_time": 19260.0,
      "text": "is I would start with a simple request."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20260.0,
      "end_time": 22260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like all of you"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22260.0,
      "end_time": 24260.0,
      "text": "to pause for a moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24260.0,
      "end_time": 26260.0,
      "text": "you wretched weaklings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26260.0,
      "end_time": 29260.0,
      "text": "and take stock of your miserable existence."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29260.0,
      "end_time": 31260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33260.0,
      "end_time": 35260.0,
      "text": "Now that was the advice"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35260.0,
      "end_time": 37260.0,
      "text": "that St. Benedict gave his rather startled followers"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37260.0,
      "end_time": 39260.0,
      "text": "in the fifth century."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39260.0,
      "end_time": 41260.0,
      "text": "It was the advice that I decided to follow myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41260.0,
      "end_time": 44260.0,
      "text": "when I turned 40."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44260.0,
      "end_time": 47260.0,
      "text": "Up until that moment, I had been that classic corporate warrior --"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47260.0,
      "end_time": 49260.0,
      "text": "I was eating too much, I was drinking too much,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49260.0,
      "end_time": 51260.0,
      "text": "I was working too hard"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51260.0,
      "end_time": 53260.0,
      "text": "and I was neglecting the family."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53260.0,
      "end_time": 55260.0,
      "text": "And I decided that I would try"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55260.0,
      "end_time": 57260.0,
      "text": "and turn my life around."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57260.0,
      "end_time": 59260.0,
      "text": "In particular, I decided"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "I would try to address the thorny issue"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 64259.0,
      "text": "of work-life balance."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 64260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67260.0,
      "text": "So I stepped back from the workforce,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 67260.0,
      "end_time": 70260.0,
      "text": "and I spent a year at home"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 70260.0,
      "end_time": 73260.0,
      "text": "with my wife and four young children."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73260.0,
      "end_time": 75260.0,
      "text": "But all I learned about work-life balance"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75260.0,
      "end_time": 77260.0,
      "text": "from that year"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 77260.0,
      "end_time": 79260.0,
      "text": "was that I found it quite easy"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 79260.0,
      "end_time": 81260.0,
      "text": "to balance work and life"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 81260.0,
      "end_time": 83260.0,
      "text": "when I didn&#39;t have any work."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 83260.0,
      "end_time": 87260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 87260.0,
      "end_time": 89260.0,
      "text": "Not a very useful skill,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 89260.0,
      "end_time": 92260.0,
      "text": "especially when the money runs out."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 92260.0,
      "end_time": 94260.0,
      "text": "So I went back to work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 94260.0,
      "end_time": 97260.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ve spent these seven years since"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 97260.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "struggling with, studying"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 103260.0,
      "text": "and writing about work-life balance."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 103260.0,
      "end_time": 105260.0,
      "text": "And I have four observations"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 105260.0,
      "end_time": 107260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to share with you today."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 107260.0,
      "end_time": 109260.0,
      "text": "The first is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 109260.0,
      "end_time": 112260.0,
      "text": "if society&#39;s to make any progress on this issue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 112260.0,
      "end_time": 115260.0,
      "text": "we need an honest debate."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 115260.0,
      "end_time": 117260.0,
      "text": "But the trouble is"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 117260.0,
      "end_time": 119260.0,
      "text": "so many people talk so much rubbish"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 119260.0,
      "end_time": 121260.0,
      "text": "about work-life balance."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 122260.0,
      "end_time": 124260.0,
      "text": "All the discussions about flexi-time"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 127260.0,
      "text": "or dress-down Fridays"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 127260.0,
      "end_time": 129259.0,
      "text": "or paternity leave"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 129258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132260.0,
      "text": "only serve to mask the core issue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 132260.0,
      "end_time": 134260.0,
      "text": "which is"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 134260.0,
      "end_time": 137260.0,
      "text": "that certain job and career choices"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 137260.0,
      "end_time": 140260.0,
      "text": "are fundamentally incompatible"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 140260.0,
      "end_time": 142260.0,
      "text": "with being meaningfully engaged"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 142260.0,
      "end_time": 144260.0,
      "text": "on a day-to-day basis"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 144260.0,
      "end_time": 146260.0,
      "text": "with a young family."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 148260.0,
      "end_time": 150260.0,
      "text": "Now the first step in solving any problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 150260.0,
      "end_time": 153260.0,
      "text": "is acknowledging the reality of the situation you&#39;re in."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 153260.0,
      "end_time": 157260.0,
      "text": "And the reality of the society that we&#39;re in"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 157260.0,
      "end_time": 159260.0,
      "text": "is there are thousands and thousands"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 159260.0,
      "end_time": 161260.0,
      "text": "of people out there"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 161260.0,
      "end_time": 165260.0,
      "text": "leading lives of quiet, screaming desperation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 167260.0,
      "text": "where they work long, hard hours"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 167260.0,
      "end_time": 169260.0,
      "text": "at jobs they hate"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 169260.0,
      "end_time": 171260.0,
      "text": "to enable them to buy things they don&#39;t need"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 171260.0,
      "end_time": 173260.0,
      "text": "to impress people they don&#39;t like."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 173260.0,
      "end_time": 175260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 175260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 182260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s my contention that going to work on Friday in jeans and [a] T-shirt"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 182260.0,
      "end_time": 184260.0,
      "text": "isn&#39;t really getting to the nub of the issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 184260.0,
      "end_time": 187260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 190260.0,
      "text": "The second observation I&#39;d like to make"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 190260.0,
      "end_time": 192260.0,
      "text": "is we need to face the truth"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 192260.0,
      "end_time": 194260.0,
      "text": "that governments and corporations"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 194260.0,
      "end_time": 197260.0,
      "text": "aren&#39;t going to solve this issue for us."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 197260.0,
      "end_time": 199260.0,
      "text": "We should stop looking outside."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 199260.0,
      "end_time": 201260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s up to us as individuals"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 201260.0,
      "end_time": 204260.0,
      "text": "to take control and responsibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 204260.0,
      "end_time": 207260.0,
      "text": "for the type of lives that we want to lead."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 207260.0,
      "end_time": 209260.0,
      "text": "If you don&#39;t design your life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 209260.0,
      "end_time": 212260.0,
      "text": "someone else will design it for you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 212260.0,
      "end_time": 214260.0,
      "text": "and you may just not like"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 214260.0,
      "end_time": 216260.0,
      "text": "their idea of balance."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 219260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s particularly important --"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 219260.0,
      "end_time": 221260.0,
      "text": "this isn&#39;t on the World Wide Web, is it? I&#39;m about to get fired --"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 221260.0,
      "end_time": 223260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s particularly important"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 223260.0,
      "end_time": 226260.0,
      "text": "that you never put the quality of your life"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 226260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "in the hands of a commercial corporation."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 230260.0,
      "end_time": 233260.0,
      "text": "Now I&#39;m not talking here just about the bad companies --"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 233260.0,
      "end_time": 236260.0,
      "text": "the \"abattoirs of the human soul,\" as I call them."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 236260.0,
      "end_time": 238260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 238260.0,
      "end_time": 241260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m talking about all companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 241260.0,
      "end_time": 243260.0,
      "text": "Because commercial companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 243260.0,
      "end_time": 245260.0,
      "text": "are inherently designed"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 245260.0,
      "end_time": 247260.0,
      "text": "to get as much out of you [as]"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 247260.0,
      "end_time": 249260.0,
      "text": "they can get away with."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 249260.0,
      "end_time": 251260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s in their nature; it&#39;s in their DNA;"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 251260.0,
      "end_time": 253260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s what they do --"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 253260.0,
      "end_time": 256260.0,
      "text": "even the good, well-intentioned companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 256260.0,
      "end_time": 258260.0,
      "text": "On the one hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 258260.0,
      "end_time": 260260.0,
      "text": "putting childcare facilities in the workplace"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 260260.0,
      "end_time": 262260.0,
      "text": "is wonderful and enlightened."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 262260.0,
      "end_time": 264260.0,
      "text": "On the other hand, it&#39;s a nightmare --"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 264260.0,
      "end_time": 267260.0,
      "text": "it just means you spend more time at the bloody office."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 269260.0,
      "end_time": 271260.0,
      "text": "We have to be responsible"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 271260.0,
      "end_time": 273260.0,
      "text": "for setting and enforcing"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 273260.0,
      "end_time": 276260.0,
      "text": "the boundaries that we want in our life."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 277260.0,
      "end_time": 279260.0,
      "text": "The third observation is"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 279260.0,
      "end_time": 281260.0,
      "text": "we have to be careful"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 281260.0,
      "end_time": 284260.0,
      "text": "with the time frame that we choose"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 284260.0,
      "end_time": 287260.0,
      "text": "upon which to judge our balance."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 288260.0,
      "end_time": 290260.0,
      "text": "Before I went back to work"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 290260.0,
      "end_time": 292260.0,
      "text": "after my year at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 292260.0,
      "end_time": 294260.0,
      "text": "I sat down"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 294260.0,
      "end_time": 296260.0,
      "text": "and I wrote out"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 296260.0,
      "end_time": 299260.0,
      "text": "a detailed, step-by-step description"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 299260.0,
      "end_time": 302260.0,
      "text": "of the ideal balanced day"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 302260.0,
      "end_time": 304260.0,
      "text": "that I aspired to."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 304260.0,
      "end_time": 307260.0,
      "text": "And it went like this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 307260.0,
      "end_time": 309260.0,
      "text": "wake up well rested"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 309260.0,
      "end_time": 311260.0,
      "text": "after a good night&#39;s sleep."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 311260.0,
      "end_time": 313260.0,
      "text": "Have sex."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 314260.0,
      "end_time": 316260.0,
      "text": "Walk the dog."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 316260.0,
      "end_time": 319260.0,
      "text": "Have breakfast with my wife and children."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 319260.0,
      "end_time": 321260.0,
      "text": "Have sex again."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 321260.0,
      "end_time": 324260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 324260.0,
      "end_time": 327260.0,
      "text": "Drive the kids to school on the way to the office."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 327260.0,
      "end_time": 329260.0,
      "text": "Do three hours&#39; work."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 329260.0,
      "end_time": 332260.0,
      "text": "Play a sport with a friend at lunchtime."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 332260.0,
      "end_time": 334260.0,
      "text": "Do another three hours&#39; work."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 334260.0,
      "end_time": 337260.0,
      "text": "Meet some mates in the pub for an early evening drink."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 338260.0,
      "end_time": 340260.0,
      "text": "Drive home for dinner"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 340260.0,
      "end_time": 343260.0,
      "text": "with my wife and kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 343260.0,
      "end_time": 346260.0,
      "text": "Meditate for half an hour."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 346260.0,
      "end_time": 348260.0,
      "text": "Have sex."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 348260.0,
      "end_time": 351260.0,
      "text": "Walk the dog. Have sex again."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 351260.0,
      "end_time": 354260.0,
      "text": "Go to bed."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 354260.0,
      "end_time": 359260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 359260.0,
      "end_time": 361260.0,
      "text": "How often do you think I have that day?"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 361260.0,
      "end_time": 364260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 364260.0,
      "end_time": 366260.0,
      "text": "We need to be realistic."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 366260.0,
      "end_time": 368260.0,
      "text": "You can&#39;t do it all in one day."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 368260.0,
      "end_time": 371260.0,
      "text": "We need to elongate the time frame"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 371260.0,
      "end_time": 373260.0,
      "text": "upon which we judge the balance in our life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 373260.0,
      "end_time": 375260.0,
      "text": "but we need to elongate it"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 375260.0,
      "end_time": 377260.0,
      "text": "without falling into the trap"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 377260.0,
      "end_time": 380260.0,
      "text": "of the \"I&#39;ll have a life when I retire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 380260.0,
      "end_time": 382260.0,
      "text": "when my kids have left home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 382260.0,
      "end_time": 385260.0,
      "text": "when my wife has divorced me, my health is failing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 385260.0,
      "end_time": 387260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve got no mates or interests left.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 387260.0,
      "end_time": 389260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 389260.0,
      "end_time": 392260.0,
      "text": "A day is too short; \"after I retire\" is too long."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 392260.0,
      "end_time": 395260.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s got to be a middle way."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 396260.0,
      "end_time": 398260.0,
      "text": "A fourth observation:"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 398260.0,
      "end_time": 400260.0,
      "text": "We need to approach balance"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 400260.0,
      "end_time": 403260.0,
      "text": "in a balanced way."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 403260.0,
      "end_time": 405260.0,
      "text": "A friend came to see me last year --"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 405260.0,
      "end_time": 408260.0,
      "text": "and she doesn&#39;t mind me telling this story -- a friend came to see me last year"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 408260.0,
      "end_time": 410260.0,
      "text": "and said, \"Nigel, I&#39;ve read your book."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 410260.0,
      "end_time": 413260.0,
      "text": "And I realize that my life is completely out of balance."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 413260.0,
      "end_time": 416260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s totally dominated by work."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 416260.0,
      "end_time": 419260.0,
      "text": "I work 10 hours a day; I commute two hours a day."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 419260.0,
      "end_time": 421260.0,
      "text": "All of my relationships have failed."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 421260.0,
      "end_time": 423260.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s nothing in my life"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 423260.0,
      "end_time": 425260.0,
      "text": "apart from my work."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 425260.0,
      "end_time": 428260.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;ve decided to get a grip and sort it out."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 428260.0,
      "end_time": 430260.0,
      "text": "So I joined a gym.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 430260.0,
      "end_time": 433260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 433260.0,
      "end_time": 436260.0,
      "text": "Now I don&#39;t mean to mock,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 436260.0,
      "end_time": 440260.0,
      "text": "but being a fit 10-hour-a-day office rat"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 440260.0,
      "end_time": 443260.0,
      "text": "isn&#39;t more balanced; it&#39;s more fit."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 443260.0,
      "end_time": 445260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 445260.0,
      "end_time": 448260.0,
      "text": "Lovely though physical exercise may be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 448260.0,
      "end_time": 450260.0,
      "text": "there are other parts to life --"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 450260.0,
      "end_time": 452260.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s the intellectual side; there&#39;s the emotional side;"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 452260.0,
      "end_time": 454260.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s the spiritual side."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 454260.0,
      "end_time": 456260.0,
      "text": "And to be balanced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 456260.0,
      "end_time": 458260.0,
      "text": "I believe we have to attend"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 458260.0,
      "end_time": 460260.0,
      "text": "to all of those areas --"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 460260.0,
      "end_time": 463260.0,
      "text": "not just do 50 stomach crunches."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 463260.0,
      "end_time": 465260.0,
      "text": "Now that can be daunting."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 465260.0,
      "end_time": 468260.0,
      "text": "Because people say, \"Bloody hell mate, I haven&#39;t got time to get fit."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 468260.0,
      "end_time": 470260.0,
      "text": "You want me to go to church and call my mother.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 470260.0,
      "end_time": 472260.0,
      "text": "And I understand."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 472260.0,
      "end_time": 475260.0,
      "text": "I truly understand how that can be daunting."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 475260.0,
      "end_time": 478260.0,
      "text": "But an incident that happened a couple of years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 478260.0,
      "end_time": 480260.0,
      "text": "gave me a new perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 480260.0,
      "end_time": 483260.0,
      "text": "My wife, who is somewhere in the audience today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 483260.0,
      "end_time": 486260.0,
      "text": "called me up at the office"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 486260.0,
      "end_time": 489260.0,
      "text": "and said, \"Nigel, you need to pick our youngest son\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 489260.0,
      "end_time": 491260.0,
      "text": "Harry -- \"up from school.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 491260.0,
      "end_time": 494260.0,
      "text": "Because she had to be somewhere else with the other three children for that evening."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 494260.0,
      "end_time": 497260.0,
      "text": "So I left work an hour early that afternoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 497260.0,
      "end_time": 500260.0,
      "text": "and picked Harry up at the school gates."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 501260.0,
      "end_time": 503260.0,
      "text": "We walked down to the local park,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 503260.0,
      "end_time": 506260.0,
      "text": "messed around on the swings, played some silly games."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 506260.0,
      "end_time": 509260.0,
      "text": "I then walked him up the hill to the local cafe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 509260.0,
      "end_time": 512260.0,
      "text": "and we shared a pizza for two,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 512260.0,
      "end_time": 514260.0,
      "text": "then walked down the hill to our home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 514260.0,
      "end_time": 516260.0,
      "text": "and I gave him his bath"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 516260.0,
      "end_time": 519260.0,
      "text": "and put him in his Batman pajamas."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 519260.0,
      "end_time": 521260.0,
      "text": "I then read him a chapter"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 521260.0,
      "end_time": 524260.0,
      "text": "of Roald Dahl&#39;s \"James and the Giant Peach.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 524260.0,
      "end_time": 526260.0,
      "text": "I then put him to bed, tucked him in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 526260.0,
      "end_time": 528260.0,
      "text": "gave him a kiss on his forehead and said, \"Goodnight, mate,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 528260.0,
      "end_time": 530260.0,
      "text": "and walked out of his bedroom."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 530260.0,
      "end_time": 532260.0,
      "text": "As I was walking out of his bedroom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 532260.0,
      "end_time": 535260.0,
      "text": "he said, \"Dad?\" I went, \"Yes, mate?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 535260.0,
      "end_time": 537260.0,
      "text": "He went, \"Dad, this has been the best day"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 537260.0,
      "end_time": 540260.0,
      "text": "of my life, ever.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 542260.0,
      "end_time": 545260.0,
      "text": "I hadn&#39;t done anything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 545260.0,
      "end_time": 548260.0,
      "text": "hadn&#39;t taken him to Disney World or bought him a Playstation."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 548260.0,
      "end_time": 550260.0,
      "text": "Now my point is"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 550260.0,
      "end_time": 553260.0,
      "text": "the small things matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 553260.0,
      "end_time": 555260.0,
      "text": "Being more balanced"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 555260.0,
      "end_time": 558260.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t mean dramatic upheaval in your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 558260.0,
      "end_time": 560260.0,
      "text": "With the smallest investment"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 560260.0,
      "end_time": 562260.0,
      "text": "in the right places,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 562260.0,
      "end_time": 565260.0,
      "text": "you can radically transform the quality of your relationships"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 565260.0,
      "end_time": 567260.0,
      "text": "and the quality of your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 567260.0,
      "end_time": 569260.0,
      "text": "Moreover, I think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 569260.0,
      "end_time": 572260.0,
      "text": "it can transform society."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 572260.0,
      "end_time": 574260.0,
      "text": "Because if enough people do it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 574260.0,
      "end_time": 577260.0,
      "text": "we can change society&#39;s definition of success"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 577260.0,
      "end_time": 580260.0,
      "text": "away from the moronically simplistic notion"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 580260.0,
      "end_time": 584260.0,
      "text": "that the person with the most money when he dies wins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 584260.0,
      "end_time": 587260.0,
      "text": "to a more thoughtful and balanced definition"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 587260.0,
      "end_time": 591260.0,
      "text": "of what a life well lived looks like."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 591260.0,
      "end_time": 593260.0,
      "text": "And that, I think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 593260.0,
      "end_time": 595260.0,
      "text": "is an idea worth spreading."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 595260.0,
      "end_time": 598260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}